        <div class="msgSubject">A Beginner's Guide to Eorzea (11/22/2010）</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-22 04:18:36   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1290421116283563386" id="quote-1290421116283563386" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1290421116283563386" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=152&amp;mid=1290421116283563386&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1290421116283563386&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1290421116283563386" onclick="followToggle('add','1290421116283563386')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
